Debian-Alwinner Hardware
========================

Install Debian on your arm-hf Hardware

https://wiki.debian.org/InstallingDebianOn/Allwinner

http://ftp.uk.debian.org/debian/dists/stretch/main/installer-armhf/current/images/netboot/SD-card-images/


Edge-native
===========

Welcome to Edge-native, the Smart-SARAH Edge-Router distribution.

The official installer supports Linux on arm-hf architectures.

6lowpan-Stick
-------------

Needs a USB-6LoWPAN-Stick with slip-radio firmware and 38400 Boud

Features
--------

  * IPv6 support

What Edge-native contains
-------------------------------

Raspi-Edge currently comes with the following software:

  * boarder-router.native
  * radvd
  

Quick introduction
------------------

The following example illustrates how simple Edge-native is to use. First install the package matching your operating system:

# sudo sh edge_install_script.sh

have fun :-)
